            bindings = <
                      &kp EXCL          &kp AT         &kp HASH   &kp DLLR              &kp PRCNT    &kp CARET  &kp AMPS               &kp STAR   &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp BSLH
                      &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp LS(MINUS)  &kp MINUS  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &trans       &trans     &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp EQUAL  &kp LS(EQUAL)     &kp BACKSLASH
&kp NON_US_BACKSLASH  &kp N1            &kp N2         &kp N3     &kp N4                &kp N5       &kp N6     &kp N7                 &kp N8     &kp N9            &kp N0         &kp SQT
                                                       &trans     &trans                &trans       &trans     &trans                 &trans
